blueprint.label: 4-Car MULTI-Provider
blueprint.description:
This station can provide multiple items, each with a separate minimum loading (configured in the PRVD combinator).  Logic ensures that it won't exceed the request and risk leaving inserters hanging with items to drop in to the next train.

IMPORTANT: If any of the provided items can be loaded into engines (coal, etc.) then the min-length must be changed to 6 (2 engines + 4 cars) or inserters will be left hanging and mess up all trains that come after.
